Known from the department of 
<collectingRegion box="[715,881,369,395]" country="Peru" name="Madre de Dios" pageId="7" pageNumber="378">Madre de Dios</collectingRegion>
in 
<collectingCountry box="[917,972,369,395]" name="Peru" pageId="7" pageNumber="378">Peru</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="7.[151,1436,153,431]" box="[199,1338,404,431]" pageId="7" pageNumber="378">
